snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Help Wanted 2 - Flat Version Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Fazbear Entertainment is on the hunt for a dedicated employee! Think you have what it takes?🐻
Five Nights at Freddy’s: Help Wanted 2’s Flat Mode is coming to PS5 and Steam June 20th.
